---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-ink via-[#1a2332] to-ink text-white min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-32">
  <div class="glow-orb w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-teal/[0.07] top-[-150px] right-[-150px]"></div>
  <div class="glow-orb w-[350px] h-[350px] bg-amber/[0.05] bottom-[-100px] left-[-100px]"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10 space-y-14 md:space-y-18">
    <p class="fluid-heading-md font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 reveal">
      Tidak apa-apa jika hari ini belum memahami semuanya.
    </p>

    <p class="fluid-heading-md font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
      Tidak apa-apa jika masih sering salah.
    </p>

    <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-amber/50 to-transparent mx-auto reveal"></div>

    <p class="fluid-heading-md font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
      Karena setiap pencapaian besar selalu dimulai dari satu langkah kecil.
    </p>

    <div class="pt-6 reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.3s">
      <h3 class="fluid-heading-lg leading-snug">
        Dan langkah itu dimulai dengan <span class="gradient-amber text-glow-amber">merintis nalar.</span>
      </h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
